## 14. Server-Wartung (Administratoren)

### Docker-Container starten/stoppen:

```bash
# Alle Container starten
docker-compose -f deployment/docker-compose.server.yml up -d

# Container neustarten
docker-compose -f deployment/docker-compose.server.yml restart

# Logs anzeigen
docker logs -f openclaw-backend
```

### Backup erstellen:

```bash
# Backup via API
curl -X POST http://35.195.246.45:3002/api/backup/create

# Manuell auf Server
docker exec openclaw-postgres pg_dump -U openclaw openclaw_db > /root/openclaw-backups/backup.sql
```

